{"tid":1314151,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜、志效唱一唱哭了！TWICE全員淚崩喊話","createTime":"2019-07-14T05:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T13:04:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"442c809c00879260c1c4a21b31218d5737c3b11d","tid":1314151,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:13:18.000Z","msg":"南韓女團TWICE傷兵累累，多名成員身體狀況不佳，雖然今（13日）晚間多賢順利與成員一起參加新加坡的演唱會，但還是少了MINA。表演到一半，SANA、多賢、志效看了粉絲應援影片後潸然淚下，子瑜走到舞台中間時也哭了，娜璉答應歌迷，「我們會永遠9個人」，逼哭現場鐵粉！<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D_WjXKzVUAEdMnG?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD_WjXKzVUAEdMnG%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=39f62366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE今晚正在新加坡舉辦巡迴演唱會，MINA傳出疑似患有舞台恐慌症，因健康問題暫停活動，但成員們紛紛上場分擔MINA在每首歌需要表演的部分，展現絕佳的團隊默契。<br />\n<br />\n不過站到舞台中央，當TWICE唱到了《After Moon》時，不少粉絲亮起了MINA應援色的手燈（「TWICE LOVELYS」的對應顏色），成員開始唱到落淚，包含子瑜、志效都被看到在擦眼淚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jyolo2/status/1149980931987345408?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1149980931987345408&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190713%2F1489449.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjyolo2%2Fstatus%2F1149980931987345408%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1149980931987345408%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190713%252F1489449.htm&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPaoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=7286ee67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjyolo2%2Fstatus%2F1149980931987345408%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1149980931987345408%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190713%252F1489449.htm&h=6043aa01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jyolo2/status/1149980931987345408?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1149980931987345408&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190713%2F1489449.htm</a><br />\nTzuyu crying 😭<br />\n<br />\n在最後則是粉絲獻上驚喜應援影片，TWICE看完轉頭又瞧見粉絲手上拿著的手幅，多賢此時已經忍不住眼角的淚水，SANA也是哭到用手遮住自己的臉，幾乎全員都淚灑台上，台下則聽到不少男粉喊：「別哭！Don't Cry！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jyolo2/status/1149983538705420289?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1149983538705420289&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190713%2F1489449.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjyolo2%2Fstatus%2F1149983538705420289%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1149983538705420289%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190713%252F1489449.htm&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPaoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=850d205a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjyolo2%2Fstatus%2F1149983538705420289%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1149983538705420289%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ettoday.net%252Fnews%252F20190713%252F1489449.htm&h=563717a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/jyolo2/status/1149983538705420289?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1149983538705420289&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190713%2F1489449.htm</a><br />\nJihyo crying too😭 <br />\n多賢對粉絲說，「雖然你們感謝我們成為你們的光芒，但我也想對你們這樣說，你們也是我們的光芒，雖然有很多遺憾，但請等待我們以9個人回來的那天！」娜璉也說，「別忘記TWICE永遠是9個人，我們會更好、更堅強，請等著我們。」彩瑛則喊話，「就像你們想見MINA，我們也都很想念她，希望你們能等待著，大家都要健康，永遠開心就好了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334c400b9a0c266622251a4bfb77e16e00f35f14","tid":1314151,"uid":555,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T